Actress Mercy Aigbe has pledged to act in the capacity of mother-of-the-day for her fans. In a recent Instagram post, the movie star who trended last month following her second marriage to ‘D Owner’, Kasim Adeoti disclosed that her fans have been actively wooing themselves in her comment section.   Why my marriage to Kanye West failed, by Kim Kardashian     Explaining yourself to people waste of time, energy –…     How ‘Google me’ saved me in London hotel, by Bovi   Having observed the activity going on in her comment section, Hajia Minnah as she named at her Nikkah promised to fulfill the duties of mother-of-the-day for her fans who agree to get married in the process. She wrote: “Awww I see people toasting themselves in my comment section. Abeg if it leads to marriage, I promise to be the mother of the day oh!!!”